{
    "1317:0": "dhyānapaṭalama",
    "1317:1": "uddānaṃ pūrvaṃvadveditavyam|",
    "1317:2": "tatra katamo bodhisattvānāṃ dhyānasvabhāvaḥ|",
    "1317:3": "bodhisattvapiṭakaśravaṇacintāpūrvakaṃ yallaukikaṃ lokottaraṃ bodhisattvānāṃ kuśalaṃ cittaikāgryañcittasthitiḥ śamathapakṣyā vā vipaśyanāpakṣyā vā yuganaddhavāhimārgaṃ tadubhayāpakṣyā vā|",
    "1317:4": "ayaṃ bodhisattvānāṃ dhyānasvabhāvo veditavyaḥ|",
    "1317:5": "tatra katamadbodhisattvānāṃ sarvaṃdhyānam|",
    "1317:6": "tad dvividhaṃ draṣṭavyam|",
    "1317:7": "laukikaṃ lokottarañca|",
    "1317:8": "tatpunaryathāyogaṃ trividhaṃ veditavyam|",
    "1317:9": "dṛṣṭadharmasukhavihārāya dhyānaṃ bodhisattva-samādhiguṇanirhārāya dhyāna sattvārthakriyāyai dhyānam|",
    "1317:10": "tatra yadbodhisattvānāṃ sarvavikalpāpagataṃ kāyikacaittasikaprasrabdhijanakaṃ paramapraśāntaṃ manyanāpagatamanāsvāditaṃ sarvanimittāpagataṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:11": "idameṣāṃ dṛṣṭadharmasukhavihārāya veditavyam|",
    "1317:12": "tatra yadbodhisattvānāṃ dhyānaṃ vicitrācintyāpramāṇadaśabalagotra-saṃgṛhītasamādhinirhārāya saṃvartate|",
    "1317:13": "yeṣāṃ samādhīnāṃ sarvaśrāvakapratyekabuddhā api nāmāpi na prajānanti kutaḥ punaḥ samāpatsyante|",
    "1317:14": "yacca bodhisattvavimokṣābhibhvāyatanakṛtsnāyatanānāṃ pratisaṃvid-araṇā-praṇidhijñānādīnāṃ [guṇānāṃ] śrāvakasādhāraṇānāmabhinirhārāya saṃvartate|",
    "1317:15": "idaṃ bodhisattvasya dhyānaṃ samādhiguṇābhinirhārāya veditavyam|",
    "1317:16": "sattvārthakarmaṇi dhyānaṃ bodhisattvasyaikādaśākāraṃ pūrvavadveditavyam|",
    "1317:17": "yaddhyānaṃ niśritya bodhisattvaḥ sattvānāṃ kṛtyeṣvarthopasaṃhiteṣu sahāyībhāvaṃ gacchati|",
    "1317:18": "duḥkhamanapanayati|",
    "1317:19": "duḥkhitānāṃ nyāyamupadiśati|",
    "1317:20": "kṛtajñaḥ kṛtavedī upakāriṣu pratyupakāraṃ karoti|",
    "1317:21": "bhayebhyo rakṣati|",
    "1317:22": "vyasanasthānāṃ śokaṃ prativinodayati|",
    "1317:23": "upakaraṇavikalānāmupakaraṇopasaṃhāraṃ karoti|",
    "1317:24": "samyak pariṣadaṃ parikarṣati|",
    "1317:25": "cittamanuvartate|",
    "1317:26": "bhūtairguṇairharṣayati|",
    "1317:27": "samyak ca nigṛhṇāti|",
    "1317:28": "ṛddhyā cotrāsayatyāvarjayati ceti|",
    "1317:29": "tadaitatsarvamekadhyamabhisaṃkṣipya bodhisattvānāṃ sarvadhyānamityucyate|",
    "1317:30": "nāta uttari nāto bhūyaḥ|",
    "1317:31": "tatra katamadbodhisattvānāṃ duṣkaradhyānam|",
    "1317:32": "tat trividhaṃ draṣṭavyam|",
    "1317:33": "yadbadhisattvā udārairvicitraiḥ suparicitairdhyānavihārairabhinirhṛtairvihṛtya svecchayā tatparamaṃ dhyānasukhaṃ vyāvartya pratisaṃkhyāya sattvānukampā prabhūtāṃ sattvārthakriyāṃ sattvārthaparipākaṃ samanupaśyantaḥ kāmadhātāvupapadyante|",
    "1317:34": "idaṃ bodhisattvānāṃ prathama duṣkaradhyānaṃ veditavyam|",
    "1317:35": "punaryadbodhisattvo dhyānaṃ niśrityāprameyāsaṃkhyeyācintyānsarvaśrāvakapratyekabuddhaviṣayasamatikrāntān bodhisattvasamādhīnabhinirharati|",
    "1317:36": "idaṃ bodhisattvasya dvitīyaṃ duṣkaradhyānaṃ veditavyam|",
    "1317:37": "punaryadbodhisattvo dhyānaṃ niśrityānuttarāṃ samyaksaṃbodhimabhisaṃbudhyate|",
    "1317:38": "itīdaṃ bodhisattvasya tṛtīya duṣkaradhyānaṃ veditavyam|",
    "1317:39": "tatra katamadbodhisattvasya sarvatomukhaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:40": "taccaturvidhaṃ draṣṭavyam|",
    "1317:41": "savitarkaṃ-savicāraṃ [vivekajaṃ samādhija] prītisahagataṃ sāta-sukhasahagatamupekṣāsahagata ca|",
    "1317:42": "tatra katamadbodhisattvasya satpuruṣadhyānam|",
    "1317:43": "tatpañcavidhaṃ draṣṭavyam|",
    "1317:44": "anākhāditaṃ maitrīsahagataṃ karuṇāsahagataṃ muditāsahagatamupekṣāsahagatañca|",
    "1317:45": "tatra katamadbodhisattvasya sarvākāra-dhyānam|",
    "1317:46": "tatṣaḍvidhaṃ [saptavidhaṃ]caikadhyamabhisaṃkṣipya trayodaśavidhaṃ veditavyam|",
    "1317:47": "kuśalaṃ dhyānamavyākṛtaṃ ca nirmitanirmāṇāya dhyānaṃ śamathapakṣyaṃ vipaśyanāpakṣyaṃ svaparārthasamyagupanidhyānāya dhyānaṃ abhijñāprabhāvaguṇarnirhārāya dhyānaṃ nāmālambanaṃmarthālambanaṃ śamathanimittālambanaṃ pragrahanimittālambanamupekṣānimittālambanaṃ [dṛṣṭadharmasukha] vihārāya parārthakriyāyai ca dhyānam|",
    "1317:48": "itīdaṃ trayodaśākāraṃ bodhisattvānāṃ dhyānaṃ sarvākāramityucyate|",
    "1317:49": "tatra katamadbodhisattvasya vighātārthikadhyānam|",
    "1317:50": "tadaṣṭavidhaṃ draṣṭavyam|",
    "1317:51": "viṣāśani viṣamajvarabhūtagrahādyupadravasaṃśamakānāṃ siddhaye mantrāṇāmadhiṣṭhāyakaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:52": "dhātubhaiṣamyajātānāñca vyādhīnāṃ vividhānāṃ vyupaśamāya dhyānam|",
    "1317:53": "durbhikṣeṣu mahārauraveṣu pratyupasthiteṣu vṛṣṭinirhārakaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:54": "vividhebhyo bhayebhyo manuṣyāmanuṣyakṛtebhyo jalasthalagatebhyaḥ samyak paritrāṇā dhyayānam|",
    "1317:55": "tathā bhojanapānahīnānāmaṭavīkāntāragatānāṃ bhojanapānopasaṃhārāya dhyānam|",
    "1317:56": "bhogavihīnānāṃ vineyānāṃ bhogopasahārāya dhyānam|",
    "1317:57": "daśasu dikṣu pramattānāṃ sattvānāṃ samyaksaṃbodhanāya dhyānam|",
    "1317:58": "utpannotpannānāñca sattvakṛtyānāṃ samyak kriyāyai dhyānam|",
    "1317:59": "tatra katamadbodhisattvasyehāmutrasukhaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:60": "tannavavidhaṃ draṣṭavyam|",
    "1317:61": "ṛddhiprātihāryeṇa sattvānāṃ vinayāya dhyānam|",
    "1317:62": "ādeśanāprātihāryeṇānuśāstiprātihāryeṇa sattvānāṃ vinayāya dhyānam|",
    "1317:63": "pāpaśāriṇāmapāyabhūmividarśanaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:64": "naṣṭapratibhānānāṃ sattvānāṃ pratibhānopasaṃhārāya dhyānam|",
    "1317:65": "muṣitasmṛtīnāṃ sattvānāṃ smṛtyupasaṃhārāya dhyānam|",
    "1317:66": "aviparītaśāsrakāvyamātṛkānibandhavyavasthānāya saddharmacirasthitikatāyai dhyānam|",
    "1317:67": "laukikānāṃ śilpakarmasthānānāmarthopasaṃhitānāṃ sattvānugrāhakāṇāṃ lipigaṇananyasanasaṃkhyāmudrādīnāṃ mañcapīṭhacchatropānahādīnāñca vicitrāṇāṃ vividhānāṃ bhāṇḍopaskarāṇāmanupravartakaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:68": "apāyabhūmyupapannānāñca sattvānāṃ tat kālāpāyikaduḥkhapratiprasrambhaṇatāyai raśmipramocakaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:69": "tatra katamadbodhisattvasya viśuddhaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:70": "taddaśavidhaṃ draṣṭavyam|",
    "1317:71": "laukikyā śuddhyā [vi] śuddhamanāsvāditaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:72": "akliṣṭaṃ lokottarayā śuddhyā [vi] śuddhaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:73": "prayogaśuddhyā [vi] śuddhaṃ maulaviśuddhyā (vi)",
    "1317:74": "śuddhaṃ maulaviśeṣottaraviśuddhyā viśuddhaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:75": "praveśasthitivyutthānavaśitāviśuddhyā viśuddhaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:76": "dhyānavyāvartane punaḥ samādapanavaśitā-viśuddhyā viśuddhaṃ dhyānam abhijñāvikurvaṇavaśitā-viśuddhyā viśuddhaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:77": "sarvadṛṣṭigatāpagamaviśuddhyā viśuddhaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:78": "kleśajñeyāvaraṇaprahāṇaviśuddhyā ca viśuddhaṃ dhyānam|",
    "1317:79": "ityetaddhyānamaprameya bodhisattvānāṃ mahābodhiphalaṃ yadāśritya bodhisattvā dhyānapāramitāṃ paripūrya anuttarāṃ samyaksaṃbodhimabhisambuddhavanto'bhisaṃ [bhotsyante'bhisaṃ] budhyante ca|",
    "1317:80": "iti bodhisattvabhūmāvādhāre yogasthāne trayodaśamaṃ dhyānapaṭalam|"
}